			<text>[CASUAL MODE: A mode for people who just want to experience the gameplay in a relaxed way]
			Starting scrap: 50~
			Starting fuel: 25{
			
			The Rebel ship at the sector one exit will not be an Elite.
			Multiverse Renegades minibosses will never spawn, and Federation Outposts give free repairs.
			The Traveling Merchant always gives a sizable free gift, is weaker, and drops a powerful Energy Shield augment if killed.
			Will reduce the difficulty of the True Ending.</text>
