			Starting scrap: 20~
			Starting fuel: 12{
			
			A weaker Rebel Elite will await you at the sector one exit.
			Renegade minibosses will spawn with moderate strength and take scrap as tribute.
			The Traveling Merchant gives a small free gift in the Drop Point and Last Stand, and drops a powerful Energy Shield augment if killed.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="SET_DIFFICULTY_NORMAL"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Challenge.</text>
		<event>
			<text>[CHALLENGE MODE: A mode for people looking for a harder challenge, but without things getting too out of hand]
