			Starting fuel: 10{
			
			The Rebel fleet gains a 1 jump boost. Increases difficulty of the Elite at the sector one exit.
			Renegades Bosses are buffed and take crew as tribute, Last Stand repair beacons will always be under attack by Elite Rebels.
			The Traveling Merchant never gives any gifts, is stronger, and drops a powerful weapon under most circumstances if killed.
			Will increase the difficulty of the True Ending.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="SET_DIFFICULTY_CHALLENGE"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Extreme.</text>
		<event>
			<text>[EXTREME MODE: Bored of things being too easy? Looking to make your life hell? This might be the mode for you.]
