<event name="SOLAR_WRECK" unique="true">
	<text>The charred remains of a ship well beyond recognition drifts near the sun at this beacon. It won't be long until the strong gravitational pull of the star pulls it in, but there might be enough time for you to salvage a chunk of it.</text>
	<environment type="sun"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
