			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Check the storage.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<eventList name="CIVILIAN_EXPLODED_HELP">
	<event>
		<text>It appears the civilians didn't survive, though whether the lack of oxygen or the explosion was the culprit you aren't sure. You scrap what little remains of the ship and move on.</text>
		<autoReward level="LOW">standard</autoReward>
	</event>
	<event>
		<text>It appears only one civilian survived the explosion. They're grateful for your help and offer to serve on your ship.</text>
		<crewMember amount="1"/>
	</event>
	<event>
		<text>You board the ship to find a gang of pirates onboard! They must have killed the civilians and accidentally destroyed the reactor.</text>
		<boarders min="2" max="3" class="random"/>
	</event>
</eventList>
<eventList name="CIVILIAN_EXPLODED_SCAN">
	<event>
		<text>It appears the civilians didn't survive, though whether the lack of oxygen or the explosion was the culprit you aren't sure. You scrap what little remains of the ship and move on.</text>
