<event name="CIVILIAN_ASTEROID_APPROACHING" unique="true">
	<text>You're hailed by a desperate Civilian station. "Please, you have to help! Our scanners detect large asteroids approaching our station, but we're defenseless against them!"</text>
	<choice hidden="true">	
		<text>Protect them from the asteroids.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You find the asteroids in question. You only have so much time until they hit the station.</text>
			<ship load="SHIP_ASTEROID" hostile="true"/>
			<status type="limit" target="player" system="hacking" amount="0"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="BLUELIST_ARMOR">	
		<text>(Hull Armor) Block the asteroid with your vessel.</text>
		<event>
			<text>As the asteroid comes closer it's clear you won't get away as unscathed as you had hoped, but fortunately it's still recoverable. The station is grateful and offers a reward.</text>
			<damage amount="2" system="random" effect="breach"/>
			<autoReward level="MED">fuel</autoReward>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="BLUELIST_WEAPONS_HEAVY">	
		<text>(Heavy Weapon) Blast the asteroid.</text>
		<event>
			<text>It only takes one shot from your weapon to blast the asteroid back into space, scattering tiny chunks in all directions as if it were made of glass. The civilians in the station cheer for your quick and easy success and reward you.</text>
			<autoReward level="MED">fuel</autoReward>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">	
		<text>Too dangerous. We'll just wait for the FTL to charge.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Too dangerous. We'll just wait for the FTL to charge.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Check the storage.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="CIVILIAN_ASTEROID_APPROACHING_WIN">
	<text>"Thank you for your help! We'll have to make sure this won't happen in the future. But for now, here's payment for your help."</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">fuel</autoReward>
</event>
<event name="CIVILIAN_ASTEROID_APPROACHING_FAIL">
	<text>You were not able to stop the asteroids in time. They smash into the civilian station, sending debris in every direction. Some of it hits your hull, causing minor damage.</text>
	<damage amount="1" system="random" effect="breach"/>
	<damage amount="1" system="random" effect="breach"/>
	<damage amount="2"/>
	<instantEscape/>
</event>

